Package: univention-opendvdi-sessionbroker
Architecture: all
Depends: univention-virtual-machine-manager-daemon, mysql-server,
 python-cherrypy3, ${python:Depends}
XB-Python-Version: ${python:Versions}
Description: Univention OpenDVDI Sessionbroker
 This package contains the Univention OpenDVDI Sessionbroker.
 Upon user login via a Univention OpenDVDI client it returns
 the FQDN of the users Virtual Machine and periodically monitors
 the Session Alive Events sent by the client. The service may
 send commands back to the client via HTTPS Server-Push.
 The Sessionbroker connects to the Univention Virtual Machine
 Manager Daemon to resume OpenDVDI Desktops.

Package: univention-opendvdi-sessionbroker-client
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python:Depends}
XB-Python-Version: ${python:Versions}
Description: Univention OpenDVDI Sessionbroker Client
 This package contains the Univention OpenDVDI Sessionbroker Client.
 The Univention OpenDVDI Sessionbroker Client sends authenticated
 connect requests to the Univention OpenDVDI Sessionbroker to
 determine the FQDN of a users Virtual Machine and sends Session
 Alive Events while the OpenDVDI Session is open. Via HTTPS
 it listens for commands issued by the Sessionbroker.
